___('politics_manifesto_listening_1',       'EN', <<<EOT
This manifesto was written by listening. Prior to writing the very first word, a lot of time had already been spent talking with people from many different backgrounds about their lack of political representation. As it turns out, listening is an underrated tool, you can learn a lot about yourself and others from developing the ability to truly listen instead of simply hearing.
